description:
The boys head to Rob O'Neill's charity golf tournament in Nashville, Tennessee and mix it up with Rob, Ray "Cash" Care, NSYNC star Chris Kirkpatrick, country stars Randy Houser and Meghan Patrick, ex-NFL and USC quarterback Matt Cassel, former NFL lineman Andy Levitre, and the boys from Leatherwood Distillery.
